high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter then take a step to your right to face the left side of the stove.
Pick up the pot that's on the front left burner.
Turn left and walk to the sink then turn right to face it when you get to it.
Wash the pot in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Put the pot on the shelf with other objects on the right side of the fridge in the back right corner and close the doors.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot in the fridge.

high_descs: Make a left and walk towards the stove.
Pick up the pot sitting on the left burner on top of the stove.
Make a left and walk towards the sink.
Put the pot in the sink and rinse it, then take it back out.
Turn around and walk across the room towards the fridge.
Put the pot in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a pot from the stove to put in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the stove.
Pick up the dirty metal pot off of the front left burner of the stove.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the dirty metal pot in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn off the water and pick up the now clean metal pot.
Walk over to the fridge in the corner of the room.
Open the fridge and put the clean metal pot in the fridge, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean metal pot in the fridge.
